data.description: Stop throwing away money on rent and own your home! This charming 2-bedroom, 1 bathroom home would be perfect. This home is conveniently located just minutes from great restaurants, shopping, and local favorites in historic downtown Galesburg. This home is move-in ready with lots of style throughout! This home also boasts an oversized backyard with a patio for all your entertaining needs. Included with this home is a 1 stall detached garage to protect your car or hobby toys from the elements. Call today for a personal showing so you can stop paying rent and own your own home!
